{"tid":1978150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急行動】DSE考場散場派選民登記表格","createTime":"2020-04-18T13:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T11:04:12.000Z","uid":353200,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7f57666ea0ca9e10aa55156ca79b3832f53f33ae","tid":1978150,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:10:30.000Z","msg":"Dse就快開考<br />\n估計大約有3萬名校生今年滿18歲<br />\n呼籲各位揾時間去派選民登記表格<br />\n立法會選民登記截止日期2020年5月2日， 我哋大概只係得五日可以行動， 咁耐都冇行動， 希望各位真係幫下手.<br />\n<br />\n24/4（星期五） 8:30 - 12:30  1,2 視覺藝術 （一）及（二）<br />\n25/4（星期六） 8:30 - 10:30  綜合科學 （一）  11:15 - 12:45  綜合科學 （二）<br />\n25/4 8:30 - 11:00  1 化學 （一） 11:45 - 12:45  化學 （二）<br />\n25/4  8:30 - 10:10  組合科學（化學）<br />\n27/4  8:30 - 10:30  通識教育（一）<br />\n27/14 11:15 - 12:30  通識教育（二）<br />\n28/4 8:30 - 10:00 英國語文 （一）<br />\n28/4 11:00 - 13:00 英國語文 （二）<br />\n29/4（星期三） 9:15 - 12:10* 英國語文 （三）（聆聽及綜合能力考核）<br />\n2/5（星期六） 8:30 - 10:45  數學 必修部分 （一）<br />\n2/5 11:30 - 12:45  數學 必修部分 （二）<br />\n<br />\n詳細考試日期<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/HKDSE/Exam_Timetable/2020_DSE_Timetable.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2FDocLibrary%2FHKDSE%2FExam_Timetable%2F2020_DSE_Timetable.pdf&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=2a3fefce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/HKDSE/Exam_Timetable/2020_DSE_Timetable.pdf</a><br />\n試場查詢<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/HKDSE/admin/exam_centres/exam_centres.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2Ftc%2FHKDSE%2Fadmin%2Fexam_centres%2Fexam_centres.html&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=55eed283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/HKDSE/admin/exam_centres/exam_centres.html</a><br />\n<br />\n建議大家自行<br />\n印有QRcode單張 +派選民登記表格<br />\n可循以下途徑索取表格：<br />\n1。各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=b103fb43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n2。公共屋邨辦事處（大家樓下就有）<br />\n3。選舉事務處地址：<br />\n-&gt;香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓<br />\n-&gt;九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓<br />\n只要在2020年7月25日或以前年滿18歲，今年5月2日前可登記做選民<br />\n選民登記填表機<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=d2e0beb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote</a><br />\n地方選區選民新登記申請表：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=c7ee8c33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n選民資料網上查閱系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=ddd24319\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位等考生考完之後 先派選民登記表， 費事打亂佢哋嘅節奏<br />\n<br />\n 資料來源:  黑警中肺炎死全家巴打"},{"pid":"22a4b7cc282819470ba85f8b2e3c67fa3a59227a","tid":1978150,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1e91a43b90b8b3a964105b102555efcf4eb4ea0","tid":1978150,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:23:25.000Z","msg":"喂正，DSE 同學仔一定要登記呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea8c37be39a062a6f1c72d039dbc024db744768","tid":1978150,"uid":189068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:24:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">2。公共屋邨辦事處（大家樓下就有）</span><br />\n真係當個個連登仔住公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b29802575eeb2300ccc4207f52d87295c81dfd3","tid":1978150,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:25:08.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"ee4ca3ae1f19640ba4b93b5f04e4777eda0e1a12","tid":1978150,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:25:26.000Z","msg":"點都要試"},{"pid":"6b6a64eb20204db527c703521709c82b4d6cdc39","tid":1978150,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"主科派咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n中英必考"},{"pid":"39bff26c12ab8c65faf8c68ae48141f87e09a4ec","tid":1978150,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c898e982a79d26b5faaab2164950d1aa9d3b4f0","tid":1978150,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b6a64eb20204db527c703521709c82b4d6cdc39","tid":1978150,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"主科派咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n中英必考"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"5月2號之前， 只有視覺藝術，科學化學， 英文，通識，數學只有尼幾科畀我哋去準備， 至少派埋化學科學啦， 都係出多一兩日啫"},{"pid":"c5beb746aeda89ded0099dc5361685727c245289","tid":1978150,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c898e982a79d26b5faaab2164950d1aa9d3b4f0","tid":1978150,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b6a64eb20204db527c703521709c82b4d6cdc39","tid":1978150,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"主科派咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n中英必考"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"5月2號之前， 只有視覺藝術，科學化學， 英文，通識，數學只有尼幾科畀我哋去準備， 至少派埋化學科學啦， 都係出多一兩日啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:32:25.000Z","msg":"英 通 數 必考<br />\n<br />\n集中派呢三日"},{"pid":"5e3929d91eec80dbf0797b2ab728841767f5635d","tid":1978150,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:34:33.000Z","msg":"其實唔係online登記仲方便咩？有人整咗生成器架。樓主係打算叫考生即場填完再收去幫佢地寄埋，定叫佢地自己填完自己寄？如果係前者，會變咗喺學校門前聚集喎。我唔係認同個垃圾限聚令，而係會對班考生同派嘅人有危機喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//幫幫手 唔好唔理呀 ⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n香港係屬於香港人 唔好再淨係share野就算<br />\n行動最實際多一個就多一個<br />\n<br />\n📍26-55歲選民登記全線告急唔夠7成❗<br />\n📍廢老登記全部過七成❗<br />\n📍選民登記5月2號deadline❗<br />\n📍2020年7月25日前夠18歲可登記<br />\n📍21-25歲手足好叻仔有七成二登記<br />\n<br />\n即上 hk2020.vote<br />\n選民登記5分鐘搞掂<br />\n<br />\n#手動轉<br />\n#快手<br />\n#只需5分鐘<br />\n#人哋種緊票啦//"},{"pid":"cb55cbbf29639bd41acccce902d2140505e43657","tid":1978150,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e3929d91eec80dbf0797b2ab728841767f5635d","tid":1978150,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:34:33.000Z","msg":"其實唔係online登記仲方便咩？有人整咗生成器架。樓主係打算叫考生即場填完再收去幫佢地寄埋，定叫佢地自己填完自己寄？如果係前者，會變咗喺學校門前聚集喎。我唔係認同個垃圾限聚令，而係會對班考生同派嘅人有危機喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//幫幫手 唔好唔理呀 ⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n香港係屬於香港人 唔好再淨係share野就算<br />\n行動最實際多一個就多一個<br />\n<br />\n📍26-55歲選民登記全線告急唔夠7成❗<br />\n📍廢老登記全部過七成❗<br />\n📍選民登記5月2號deadline❗<br />\n📍2020年7月25日前夠18歲可登記<br />\n📍21-25歲手足好叻仔有七成二登記<br />\n<br />\n即上 hk2020.vote<br />\n選民登記5分鐘搞掂<br />\n<br />\n#手動轉<br />\n#快手<br />\n#只需5分鐘<br />\n#人哋種緊票啦//"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:37:19.000Z","msg":"兩樣都可以， 派表格係畀佢哋拎返屋企填， 但總之要人到先囉， 始終唔肯定係咪嗰個考生都有登記. 盡量幫選戰買多個希望"},{"pid":"966e8ca50ca7ccb422205ebb508d37798e8bdb4f","tid":1978150,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:57:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55d6324b4156fbec84feeaa8b10d21202146ad5b","tid":1978150,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"876cac715efc54bc917992c5fdd6a232fb65aad8","tid":1978150,"uid":353200,"like